urls.title: Book Now Pay Later - Royal Air Maroc
urls.description: Add your trip to the cart just like you normally woould. When you are ready to book choose Uplift as your form of payment Provide a few pieces of information and receive a quick decision Enjoy your trip now and pay for it over time with low monthly installments What is Uplift? Uplift gives you the freedom to book travel now and pay over time with simple fixed installments. Some plans include interest while some are interest-free. When you’re ready to checkout, just select “Uplift” as your payment method,

data.text:

Vous pouvez désormais acheter votre billet et payer plus tard sur notre site web.
 
Pour en savoir plus : https://t.co/p2D3nB9gg6
